        "content": "<p>The original example in this thread is now supported in Lean 4.<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/f0272d930942d4974ad9cfae54b8715c97f560cc/tests/lean/run/mutualWithCompositeNames.lean#L45-L87\">https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/f0272d930942d4974ad9cfae54b8715c97f560cc/tests/lean/run/mutualWithCompositeNames.lean#L45-L87</a></p>",
