    {
        "content": "<p>The dot notation works as expected, and we can also write</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">mutual</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">Foo.toString</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Foo</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">String</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">somefoo</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"foo\"</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bar</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">b.toString</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">Bar.toString</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Bar</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">String</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">somebar</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"bar\"</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">foobar</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">f.toString</span> <span class=\"bp\">++</span> <span class=\"n\">b.toString</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
